
-> Introduction Section


Group ) Within the Controllers Group, we created a SubGroup called Core.
Core will contain the Controller files for our particular Core navigation which will be Character, Location, Episode, and Settings.



Cocoa Touch ) When creating our ViewControllers, we will select Cocoa Touch Class.
The Class we will use is UIViewController.



-> Source Control Section


Documentation ) It is best practice to document our code as we go, that way we don't have the overhead of doing it later on.
